CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, September 22, 1962, pg. 15 reads:"Platform Guests were (left to right): Atty. Wendell G. Freeland, Joe Durzo, Alderman Henry Ryan, Tom Madden (general chairman), Mayor Joseph Barr, John Vandell, Judge John G. Brosky, Joseph Watts (parade marshall) and Joseph F. Watson (general chairman). - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Wendell G. Freeland, Joe Durzo, Henry Ryan, Tom Madden, Pittsburgh Mayor Joseph Barr, John Vandell, John G. Brosky, Joseph Watts, and Joseph F. Watson, standing in front of building during American Day parade, Homewood
